\f1\b0 \cf3 C\'f3 ng\uc0\u432 \u417 \u768 i la\u803 i ngh\u105 \u771 : Linh Thao l\'e0 do D\'f2ng T\'ean \'93\u273 e\u777  ra\'94 v\'e0 chi\u777  \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c d\'e0nh ri\'eang, d\'e0nh \u273 \u7885 \u770 c quy\u234 \u768 n cho D\'f2ng T\'ean. Nh\u432 ng th\u432 \u803 c ra pha\u777 i n\'f3i ng\u432 \u417 \u803 c la\u803 i m\u417 \u769 i \u273 \'fang: Linh thao \u273 \'e3 \'93\u273 e\u777  ra\'94 D\'f2ng T\'ean, v\'ec nh\u417 \u768  s\u244 \u769 ng qua kinh nghi\u7865 \u770 m Linh Thao, cho n\'ean 10 ba\u803 n s\'e1ng l\u7841 \u770 p m\u417 \u769 i c\'f3 \u273 u\u777  tinh th\u226 \u768 n, \u111 \u795 n Ch\'faa soi s\'e1ng v\'e0 nghi\u803  l\u432 \u803 c m\'e0 l\u7841 \u770 p ra D\'f2ng T\'ean. R\u244 \u768 i c\u432 \u769  nh\'ecn c\'e1c d\'f2ng kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i D\'f2ng T\'ean, c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  c\'e1c gi\'e1o d\'e2n nam n\u432 \u771  tr\'ean kh\u259 \u769 p th\u234 \u769  gi\u417 \u769 i hi\u7865 \u770 n \u273 ang gi\'fap cho nhi\u234 \u768 u anh chi\u803  cu\u777 a m\'ecnh l\'e0m quen v\'e0 th\u432 \u803 c h\'e0nh Linh Thao, th\'ec s\u101 \u771  th\u226 \u769 y r\'f5 l\'e0: kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i Linh Thao chi\u777  \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c d\'e0nh ri\'eang cho D\'f2ng T\'ean m\'e0 th\'f4i. N\u234 \u769 u trong th\u432 \u803 c t\u234 \u769 , c\'e1c tu s\u105 \u771  D\'f2ng T\'ean gi\'fap l\'e0m Linh Thao nhi\u234 \u768 u h\u111 \u795 n, th\'ec chi\u777  v\'ec trung th\'e0nh v\u417 \u769 i g\u244 \u769 c c\u7885 \u770 i tu \u273 \u432 \u769 c cu\u777 a m\'ecnh, c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  ch\u97 \u774 m lo ho\u803 c ho\u777 i, \u273 \'e0o s\'e2u v\'e0 bi\u234 \u769 t kh\'e1 v\u234 \u768  Linh Thao, n\'ean D\'f2ng T\'ean ca\u777 m th\u226 \u769 y d\u234 \u771  d\'e0ng s\u259 \u771 n s\'e0ng h\u111 \u795 n \u273 \'ea\u777  gi\'fap tha nh\'e2n trong \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng h\u432 \u417 \u769 ng \u273 \'f3. Ch\u432 \u769  kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i l\'e0 \u273 \u7885 \u770 c quy\u234 \u768 n. \
Kh\'f4ng k\'ea\uc0\u777  v\'f4 s\u244 \u769  c\'e1 nh\'e2n v\'e0 r\u226 \u769 t nhi\u234 \u768 u d\'f2ng tu trong Gi\'e1o H\u7885 \u770 i, t\u432 \u768  nhi\u234 \u768 u th\u234 \u769  ky\u777  nay, \u273 \'e3 v\'e0 \u273 ang \'e1i m\u7885 \u770  c\'f9ng s\u244 \u769 ng theo tinh th\u226 \u768 n Linh Thao, c\'f2n c\'f3 ca\u777  m\u7885 \u770 t \u273 o\'e0n th\'ea\u777  gi\'e1o d\'e2n ra\u777 i r\'e1c r\u226 \u769 t nhi\u234 \u768 u n\u111 \u795 i tr\'ean th\u234 \u769  gi\u417 \u769 i, c\u117 \u771 ng \u273 ang b\u432 \u417 \u769 c theo \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng h\u432 \u417 \u769 ng thi\'eang li\'eang cu\u777 a Linh Thao n\u432 \u771 a. \u272 \'f3 l\'e0 phong tr\'e0o Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c, v\'e0 t\u432 \u768  sau c\'f4ng \u273 \u244 \u768 ng Vatican II \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c canh t\'e2n \u273 \'ea\u777  tr\u417 \u777  th\'e0nh phong tr\'e0o C\'e1c Nh\'f3m \u272 \u417 \u768 i S\u244 \u769 ng Kit\'f4 (ti\u234 \u769 ng Ph\'e1p \'96 c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  \'dd v\'e0 T\'e2y Ban Nha \'96 vi\u234 \u769 t t\u259 \u769 t l\'e0 CVX, t\u432 \u769 c l\'e0 Communaut\'e9 de Vie Chr\'e9- tienne, c\'f2n ti\u234 \u769 ng Anh th\'ec go\u803 i l\'e0 CLC, c\'f3 ngh\u105 \u771 a l\'e0 Christian Life Community). \u272 o\'e0n th\'ea\u777  n\u226 \u768 y \u273 \'e3 c\'f4ng khai ch\'e0o \u273 \u417 \u768 i n\u97 \u774 m 1563, t\u432 \u769 c l\'e0 l\'fac Linh Thao m\u417 \u769 i \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c 41 tu\'f4\u777 i \u273 \u417 \u768 i kinh nghi\u7865 \u770 m. N\u97 \u774 m \u273 \'f3, Jean Leunis, tu s\u105 \u771  D\'f2ng T\'ean ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i Bi\u777 , tu\'f4\u777 i 28, \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 \u770 p ra nh\'f3m Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u \u273 \u226 \u768 u ti\'ean gi\u432 \u771 a c\'e1c ho\u803 c sinh tr\u432 \u417 \u768 ng D\'f2ng T\'ean ta\u803 i R\'f4ma. Sau \u273 \'f3 c\'e1c nh\'f3m kh\'e1c \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh h\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 o\'e0n ng\u117 \u771  chung quanh nh\'f3m \u273 \u226 \u768 u ti\'ean \u273 \'ea\u777  tr\u417 \u777  th\'e0nh phong tr\'e0o Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u. K\'ea\u777  ra th\'ec tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 nh\u432 \u771 ng nh\'f3m \'93\u273 a\u803 o \u273 \u432 \u769 c\'94 gi\'fap nhau s\u244 \u769 ng tinh th\u226 \u768 n Linh Thao, d\u432 \u803 a v\'e0o t\'e1c vu\u803  tr\u417 \u803  gi\'fap thi\'eang li\'eang cu\u777 a c\'e1c tu s\u105 \u771  D\'f2ng T\'ean \u273 \u226 \u768 u ti\'ean, \u273 \u7841 \u774 c bi\u7865 \u770 t l\'e0 cu\u777 a th\'e1nh Inh\'e3 Loyola; tuy nhi\'ean c\'e1c nh\'f3m n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e0n ng\u117 \u771  v\'e0 li\'ean k\u234 \u769 t v\u417 \u769 i nhau m\u7885 \u770 t c\'e1ch ch\u7841 \u774 t ch\u101 \u771  v\'e0 r\u7885 \u770 ng l\u417 \u769 n nh\u432  Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u. N\u97 \u774 m 1584, \u272 \u432 \u769 c Gi\'e1o Ho\'e0ng Gr\'eag\'f4ri\'f4 XIII \u273 \'e3 ch\'ednh th\u432 \u769 c c\'f4ng nh\u7841 \u770 n Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i l\'e0 m\u7885 \u770 t \u273 o\'e0n th\'ea\u777  cu\u777 a Gi\'e1o H\u7885 \u770 i. N\u97 \u774 m 1587, \u272 \u432 \u769 c Xist\'f4 V \u273 \'e3 cu\u777 ng c\u244 \u769  Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i v\u417 \u769 i nhi\u234 \u768 u \u273 \u7841 \u774 c \'e2n thi\'eang li\'eang. C\'e1c th\u234 \u769  ky\u777  ti\u234 \u769 p \u273 \'f3, Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u7841 \u774 t ta\u803 i nhi\u234 \u768 u n\u111 \u795 i trong th\u234 \u769  gi\u417 \u769 i c\'f4ng gi\'e1o: ta\u803 i ca\u777  nhi\u234 \u768 u n\u111 \u795 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7841 \u774 t D\'f2ng T\'ean; ch\u259 \u777 ng ha\u803 n nh\u432  ta\u803 i Vi\u7865 \u770 t Nam tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c \u273 \'e2y (tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c 1957). Ph\u226 \u768 n \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3p \u273 \u7841 \u774 c s\u259 \u769 c nh\u226 \u769 t m\'e0 Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u \u273 \'e3 mang la\u803 i cho Gi\'e1o H\u7885 \u770 i l\'e0 gi\'fap kh\u111 \u795 i d\u7841 \u770 y v\'e0 nu\'f4i d\u432 \u417 \u771 ng nhi\u234 \u768 u \u111 \u795 n go\u803 i linh mu\u803 c v\'e0 tu s\u105 \u771 ; r\u244 \u768 i t\u432 \u768  \u273 \'f3, \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap ghi th\'eam nhi\u234 \u768 u t\'ean tu\'f4\u777 i l\u432 \u768 ng danh v\'e0o ba\u777 ng v\'e0ng c\'e1c th\'e1nh. \
Xin k\'ea\uc0\u777  ra \u273 \'e2y m\u7885 \u770 t v\'e0i vi\u803  quen thu\u7885 \u770 c v\u417 \u769 i ch\'fang ta nh\u226 \u769 t, nh\u432 : Th\'e1nh Gioan Berchmans, Th\'e1nh Phanxic\'f4 de Sales, Th\'e1nh Gioan Eudes, Th\'e1nh Grignon de Montfort, Th\'e1nh Anphong- s\'f4 Liguori, Th\'e1nh Gioan B\'e1pt\'edt de la Salle, Th\'e1nh Camille de Lellis, v.v. Ng\'e0y nay, ti\u234 \u769 p tu\u803 c truy\u234 \u768 n th\u244 \u769 ng Hi\u7865 \u770 p H\u7885 \u770 i Th\'e1nh M\u226 \u771 u ng\'e0y x\u432 a, c\'e1c Nh\'f3m \u272 \u417 \u768 i S\u244 \u769 ng Kit\'f4, c\'f3 m\u7841 \u774 t ta\u803 i n\u97 \u774 m ch\'e2u, c\u117 \u771 ng \u273 ang ra s\u432 \u769 c s\u244 \u769 ng tro\u803 n tinh th\u226 \u768 n Linh Thao h\u226 \u768 u phu\u803 c vu\u803  \u273 \u259 \u769 c l\u432 \u803 c cho Ch\'faa v\'e0 anh em \u273 \u244 \u768 ng loa\u803 i cu\u777 a m\'ecnh. \
