\f1\b0 \cf3 Trong nh\uc0\u432 \u771 ng th\u7841 \u770 p ky\u777  g\u226 \u768 n \u273 \'e2y, gi\u432 \u771 a c\'e1c anh chi\u803  em ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i Vi\u7865 \u770 t s\u244 \u769 ng ta\u803 i n\u432 \u417 \u769 c ngo\'e0i, \u273 \u7841 \u774 c bi\u7865 \u770 t nh\u226 \u769 t l\'e0 ta\u803 i B\u259 \u769 c M\u121 \u771  v\'e0 \'c2u ch\'e2u, ti\u234 \u769 p theo c\'e1c kh\'f3a Linh Thao \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nhi\u234 \u768 u d\u226 \u768 n l\'ean ta\u803 i c\'e1c ch\'e2u n\'f3i tr\'ean, \u273 \'e3 th\u226 \u769 y mo\u803 c l\'ean phong tr\'e0o c\'e1c nh\'f3m Linh Thao. Gi\u432 \u771 a c\'e1c nh\'f3m Linh Thao n\'e0y, c\'f3 r\u226 \u769 t nhi\u234 \u768 u c\'e1c nh\'f3m \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e0n ng\u117 \u771  la\u803 i v\u417 \u769 i nhau theo m\u7885 \u770 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng h\u432 \u417 \u769 ng r\'f5 r\u7865 \u770 t v\'e0 trong m\u7885 \u770 t t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c ch\u7841 \u774 t ch\u101 \u771  h\u111 \u795 n: c\'e1c nh\'f3m n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c go\u803 i l\'e0 nh\'f3m \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh trong Nh\'f3m \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh l\u417 \u769 n, hay l\'e0 Phong Tr\'e0o \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh (= Ba\u803 n \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh v\u417 \u769 i Ch\'faa Kit\'f4), c\u117 \u771 ng t\u432 \u111 \u795 ng t\u432 \u803  nh\u432  phong tr\'e0o C\'e1c Nh\'f3m \u272 \u417 \u768 i S\u244 \u769 ng Kit\'f4 (CLC) n\'f3i \u417 \u777  tr\'ean. C\'f2n c\'e1c nh\'f3m kh\'e1c th\'ec t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c v\'e0 sinh hoa\u803 t t\'f9y theo nhu c\u226 \u768 u v\'e0 ho\'e0n ca\u777 nh ri\'eang. Nh\u432 ng trong th\u432 \u803 c t\u234 \u769  th\'ec kh\'f3 m\'e0 nh\u7841 \u770 n ra \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c s\u432 \u803  kh\'e1c bi\u7865 \u770 t v\u432 \u768 a n\'f3i; tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c ti\'ean l\'e0 b\u417 \u777 i v\'ec c\'e1c nh\'f3m Linh Thao \'96 c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  c\'e1c nh\'f3m vi\'ean Linh Thao \'96 v\'e0 c\'e1c nh\'f3m \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh \'96 c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  c\'e1c nh\'f3m vi\'ean \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh \'96 \u273 \u234 \u768 u nh\u259 \u768 m chung c\'f9ng m\u7885 \u770 t ti\'eau \u273 \'edch, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 tr\u417 \u777  n\'ean ba\u803 n th\'e2n cu\u777 a Ch\'faa Kit\'f4 d\u432 \u803 a theo \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng h\u432 \u417 \u769 ng Linh Thao, v\'e0 th\u432 \u769  \u273 \u234 \u769 n l\'e0 b\u417 \u777 i v\'ec nh\'f3m n\'e0y hay nh\'f3m kia \'96 nh\'f3m vi\'ean Linh Thao hay nh\'f3m vi\'ean \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh \'96 c\u117 \u771 ng th\u432 \u417 \u768 ng c\'f3 nh\u432 \u771 ng sinh ho\u803 at chung v\u417 \u769 i nhau v\'e0 kh\'e1 \u273 \u234 \u768 u \u273 \u7841 \u774 n. C\u111 \u795  quan li\'ean la\u803 c v\'e0 ph\'e1t ng\'f4n hi\u7865 \u770 n nay cu\u777 a Phong tr\'e0o \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh l\'e0 t\u417 \u768  N\u7885 \u770 i San \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh. Phong tr\'e0o \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh c\u117 \u771 ng soa\u803 n tha\u777 o nhi\u234 \u768 u t\'e0i li\u7865 \u770 u vi\u234 \u769 t ho\u7841 \u774 c ghi \'e2m \u273 \'ea\u777  gi\'fap c\'e1c anh chi\u803  em mu\u244 \u769 n t\'ecm hi\'ea\u777 u v\'e0 s\u244 \u769 ng tinh th\u226 \u768 n Linh Thao. \
T\'f3m la\uc0\u803 i, gi\u432 \u771 a cao tr\'e0o tham d\u432 \u803  c\'e1c kh\'f3a c\u226 \u769 m ph\'f2ng theo ph\u432 \u111 \u795 ng th\u432 \u769 c Linh Thao \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c ta\u803 i c\'e1c c\u7885 \u770 ng \u273 o\'e0n ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i Vi\u7865 \u770 t \u417 \u777  n\u432 \u417 \u769 c ngo\'e0i, c\'f3 th\'ea\u777  nh\u7841 \u770 n ra b\u244 \u769 n loa\u803 i th\'e0nh ph\u226 \u768 n sau \u273 \'e2y: \
1. Nh\uc0\u432 \u771 ng ba\u803 n h\'e0ng n\u97 \u774 m tham d\u432 \u803  c\u226 \u769 m ph\'f2ng Linh Thao, nh\u432 ng ho\'e0n ca\u777 nh ri\'eang kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p tham gia sinh hoa\u803 t v\u417 \u769 i m\u7885 \u770 t nh\'f3m \u273 a\u803 o \u273 \u432 \u769 c n\'e0o. \
2. Nh\uc0\u432 \u771 ng ba\u803 n thu\u7885 \u770 c c\'e1c h\u7885 \u770 i \u273 o\'e0n v\'e0 phong tr\'e0o kh\'e1c, nh\u432 ng la\u803 i mu\u244 \u769 n nh\u417 \u768  l\u244 \u769 i tu \u273 \u432 \u769 c Linh Thao m\'e0 \u273 \'e2\u777 y ma\u803 nh \u273 \u417 \u768 i s\u244 \u769 ng thi\'eang li\'eang cu\u777 a m\'ecnh, n\'ean h\'e0ng n\u97 \u774 m v\u226 \u771 n \u273 \u234 \u768 u \u273 \u7841 \u774 n tham d\u432 \u803  c\u226 \u769 m ph\'f2ng theo ph\u432 \u111 \u795 ng th\u432 \u769 c Linh Thao, \u273 \u244 \u768 ng th\u417 \u768 i v\u226 \u771 n ti\u234 \u769 p tu\u803 c sinh hoa\u803 t trong c\'e1c h\u7885 \u770 i \u273 o\'e0n ho\u7841 \u774 c phong tr\'e0o cu\u777 a m\'ecnh. \
3. Nh\uc0\u432 \u771 ng anh chi\u803  \u273 \'e3 t\u432 \u768 ng \u273 i Linh Thao, v\'e0 ti\u234 \u769 p tu\u803 c sinh ho\u803 at \u273 \u234 \u768 u \u273 \u7841 \u774 n trong c\'e1c nh\'f3m Linh Thao. \
4. V\'e0 c\'e1c anh chi\uc0\u803  thu\u7885 \u770 c c\'e1c nh\'f3m \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh. \
Nh\uc0\u432  th\u234 \u769  c\'f3 ngh\u105 \u771 a l\'e0: kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i h\u234 \u771  \u273 i Linh Thao th\'ec nh\u226 \u769 t thi\u234 \u769 t pha\u777 i v\'e0o nh\'f3m Linh Thao ho\u7841 \u774 c l\'e0 \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh, b\u417 \u777 i v\'ec \u273 i Linh Thao chi\u777  l\'e0 \u273 \'ea\u777  nh\u7841 \u770 n r\'f5 v\'e0 s\u244 \u769 ng tro\u803 n \u111 \u795 n go\u803 i kit\'f4 ri\'eang cu\u777 a m\'ecnh, ch\u432 \u769  kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i l\'e0 \u273 \'ea\u777  tr\u417 \u777  th\'e0nh th\'e0nh vi\'ean n\'e0y no\u803  cu\u777 a m\u7885 \u770 t nh\'f3m hay l\'e0 cu\u777 a m\u7885 \u770 t phong tr\'e0o n\'e0o \u273 \'f3. \
Trong khoa\uc0\u777 ng th\u417 \u768 i gian t\u432 \u768  1983 \u273 \u234 \u769 n 1997, h\u259 \u768 ng n\u97 \u774 m, tr\'ean d\u432 \u417 \u769 i 70-80% c\'e1c c\u7885 \u770 ng \u273 o\'e0n c\'f4ng gi\'e1o ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i Vi\u7865 \u770 t ta\u803 i B\u259 \u769 c M\u121 \u771  \u273 \u234 \u768 u c\'f3 t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c m\u7885 \u770 t hay nhi\u234 \u768 u kh\'f3a Linh Thao cho nh\u432 \u771 ng ai trong c\u7885 \u770 ng \u273 o\'e0n mu\u244 \u769 n tham d\u432 \u803 . D\'f9 hi\u7865 \u770 n nay, con s\u244 \u769  c\'e1c kh\'f3a c\'f3 gia\u777 m \u273 i \u273 \'f4i ch\'fat, th\'ec kh\'f4ng pha\u777 i v\'ec th\u234 \u769  m\'e0 cao tr\'e0o Linh Thao kh\'f4ng d\'e2ng th\'eam l\'ean trong di\u7865 \u770 n ph\'e2\u777 m ch\u226 \u769 t; b\u417 \u777 i con s\u244 \u769  c\'e1c kh\'f3a d\'e0i ng\'e0y v\'e0 c\'e1c tham d\u432 \u803  vi\'ean \u273 \u432 \u769 ng tu\'f4\u777 i li\'ean ti\u234 \u769 p t\u97 \u774 ng d\u226 \u768 n th\'eam. C\'e1c kh\'f3a Linh Thao n\'e0y \u273 \u234 \u768 u \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c t\'f4\u777  ch\u432 \u769 c v\u417 \u769 i s\u432 \u803  t\'e1n \u273 \u244 \u768 ng v\'e0 gi\'fap \u273 \u417 \u771  ch\'ed t\'ecnh cu\u777 a c\'e1c linh mu\u803 c qua\u777 n nhi\u7865 \u770 m c\u117 \u771 ng nh\u432  cu\u777 a gi\u417 \u769 i h\u432 \u771 u tr\'e1ch trong c\'e1c c\u7885 \u770 ng \u273 o\'e0n. \
C\'f3 m\uc0\u7885 \u770 t \u273 i\'ea\u777 m \u273 \'e1ng l\u432 u \'fd l\'e0: c\'e1c nh\'f3m Linh Thao v\'e0 phong tr\'e0o \u272 \u244 \u768 ng H\'e0nh \u273 \'e3 b\u432 \u768 ng l\'ean nh\u432  m\u7885 \u770 t \'93lu\u244 \u768 ng gi\'f3 ma\u803 nh\'94... m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7885 \u770 t s\u432 \u803  t\'ednh to\'e1n hay \u273 \u7841 \u774 t k\u234 \u769  hoa\u803 ch n\'e0o tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c ca\u777 , v\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\u432 \u768 ng l\'ean gi\u432 \u771 a nh\u432 \u771 ng ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i gi\'e1o d\'e2n tre\u777 . K\u234 \u769  hoa\u803 ch, ch\u432 \u111 \u795 ng tr\'ecnh: chi\u777  sau \u273 \'f3 c\'e1c linh mu\u803 c v\'e0 tu s\u105 \u771  m\u417 \u769 i ph\'e1c ho\u803 a ra \u273 \'ea\u777  cha\u803 y theo m\'e0 \u432 \u769 ng \u273 \'e1p nhu c\u226 \u768 u hi\u7865 \u770 n ra tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c m\u259 \u769 t, nh\u259 \u768 m h\u417 \u803 p t\'e1c v\u417 \u769 i \u111 \u795 n Ch\'faa v\'e0 v\u417 \u769 i thi\u7865 \u770 n ch\'ed cu\u777 a nh\u432 \u771 ng ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i tre\u777 . M\u432 \u417 \u768 i m\u226 \u769 y n\u97 \u774 m tr\u432 \u417 \u769 c \u273 \'e2y, ai c\'f3 th\'ea\u777  ng\u417 \u768  \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c r\u259 \u768 ng ng\'e0y nay c\'f3 m\u7885 \u770 t phong tr\'e0o b\'e0nh tr\u432 \u417 \u769 ng nhanh v\'e0 r\u7885 \u770 ng \u273 \u234 \u769 n nh\u432  th\u234 \u769 , \u273 \u234 \u769 n \u273 \u7885 \u770  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i t\u432 \u803  ho\u777 i: hi\u7865 \u770 n t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng \u226 \u769 y ch\u259 \u777 ng pha\u777 i l\'e0 d\u226 \u769 u chi\u777  cho th\u226 \u769 y r\'f5 Ch\'faa \u273 ang mu\u244 \u769 n d\'f9ng Linh Thao nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7885 \u770 t gi\u432 \u771 a nhi\u234 \u768 u ph\u432 \u111 \u795 ng th\u234 \u769  \u273 \'ea\u777  gi\'fap ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i Vi\u7865 \u770 t \u417 \u777  n\u432 \u417 \u769 c ngo\'e0i, \u273 \u7841 \u774 c bi\u7865 \u770 t l\'e0 ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i tre\u777 , s\u244 \u769 ng ma\u803 nh \u273 \u432 \u769 c tin v\'e0 l\'e0m t\'f4ng \u273 \u244 \u768  n\u111 \u795 i nh\u432 \u771 ng m\'f4i tr\u432 \u417 \u768 ng s\u244 \u769 ng m\u417 \u769 i, \u273 \u226 \u768 y kh\'f3 kh\u97 \u774 n, ch\'f4ng gai v\'e0 ca\u803 m b\u226 \u771 y gi\u432 \u771 a th\u234 \u769  gi\u417 \u769 i t\'e2n ti\u234 \u769 n ng\'e0y nay hay sao? \
N\uc0\u234 \u769 u th\u432 \u803 c s\u432 \u803  nh\u432  th\u234 \u769  th\'ec c\u226 \u768 n pha\u777 i ho\u803 c ho\u777 i v\'e0 \u273 \'e0o s\'e2u \u273 \'ea\u777  hi\'ea\u777 u bi\u234 \u769 t Linh Thao cho th\u226 \u769 u \u273 \'e1o v\'e0 s\u432 \u777  du\u803 ng Linh Thao cho \u273 i\'eau luy\u7865 \u770 n h\u226 \u768 u c\u7885 \u770 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u259 \u769 c l\u432 \u803 c v\u417 \u769 i \u111 \u795 n Ch\'faa m\'e0 gi\'fap cho anh chi\u803  em \u273 \u244 \u768 ng b\'e0o Vi\u7865 \u770 t trong n\u244 \u771  l\u432 \u803 c s\u244 \u769 ng ma\u803 nh v\'e0 s\u244 \u769 ng tro\u803 n \u273 \u417 \u768 i kit\'f4 cu\u777 a m\'ecnh. \
